Lewis Tan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lewis_Tan 0 Lewis Singwah Tan (born 1987) is a British-born American actor, model and martial artist. He is known for his roles as Zhou Cheng in Netflix's Iron Fist, Gaius Chau in the AMC martial arts drama series Into the Badlands, and Shatterstar in the film Deadpool 2.
